I want to work with kids. I want to work for the Division of Family and Children Services. I want to help kids who are hurt or not safe at home. I want to help families have better lives.

I am a good worker. I am kind. I do what is right. I want to help people get along. I want to learn more about my job so I can do it well. These are good things for a social worker. These are good things for me.

I always want to help people. I did not know what job to have. In high school and college, I saw people with problems. Some people did not want to talk about their problems. Some people used bad ways to deal with their problems. I saw these things and I went to college to study people. 

After I finished college in 2009, I met a boy. He was sixteen years old. He was sad. He was living with bad parents. I talked to the police. I told them I knew about the boy and I had studied people in college. The police asked me to talk to the boy's parents. The parents said the boy was bad. They did not want to help him. I wanted to help the boy. I wanted to be a social worker.

Social workers help people who are not treated fairly. Our society says people are important. But we all want to be the same. We do not want to be different. I am different. I like to be different. I have fought for people who are not treated fairly. I will always fight for people who are not treated fairly.

This paper looks at two ways to see sleep problems. One way is the body way. The body way looks at genes and health. The other way is the social way. The social way looks at how people live. This paper looks at both ways. It talks about studies that show how these ways can help us see sleep problems. This paper also talks about the good and bad parts of each study.

Sleep problems can be many things. Some are main sleep problems. Some are problems with other mental things. Some are problems with the body. Main sleep problems are hard to fall asleep or hard to stay asleep. These problems can be hard to stay awake. Some sleep problems happen when you dream. Others happen when you sleep walk. Some sleep problems are from other mental things. 

This paper looks at one sleep problem: insomnia. Insomnia is hard to fall asleep or stay asleep. This paper also looks at all sleep problems a little bit.

The body way says sleep problems are from genes and the body. Some parts of the brain help us sleep. These parts have special parts called receptors. Some medicines work on these receptors. A study looked at mice. The study found that these receptors help mice sleep. This means people might have the same receptors. If these receptors do not work right, people might have trouble sleeping.

The social way says sleep problems are from how people live. If someone has bad things happen, they might have trouble sleeping. If someone lives in a bad place, they might have trouble sleeping. This paper talks about how the body way and the social way can help us understand sleep problems.

This paper talks about three things. First, it gives a short look at Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD). Next, it talks about how doctors find CAPD. It looks at signs to watch for. Last, it gives ideas for teachers to help students with CAPD in a normal classroom.

CAPD is a problem with how the brain uses sound. It is not the same as hearing loss. People with CAPD can hear sounds. But, the part of the brain that changes sound into words does not work well.

Doctors first heard about CAPD in the 1950s. They called it “auditory imperception”.  Doctors started making tests for CAPD in the 1950s and 1960s.

CAPD can cause many problems. Some people have trouble finding where a sound is coming from. They may have trouble telling sounds apart. They may not hear patterns in sounds. They may not hear changes in a person’s voice. One sound may block another sound.

Doctors use tests to find CAPD. They watch how people listen. They give them tests about sound. There is no one good test to find CAPD.

Twelfth Night show us that disguise can help people trick others. But it can also make people lose who they are. It is hard to stop a trick because it can hurt people. Some people will be sad if they find out they were tricked.

Gender tricks are hard. We must ask why people do this. Why do they want to be someone else?

Viola wants to be a man to be safe. She says, "I will go to a leader in this town. I have clothes for a girl. A kind person helped me. I stayed safe to help this good man."

Viola is safe as a man. But she is alone. She misses women friends. 

Olivia thinks Viola is a man. She falls in love with Viola. She says, "Stay, my man. Cesario, husband."

Orsino likes Viola. He says, "You said you would never love a woman like me." 

Twelfth Night shows us how tricks can make people feel things they hide.  Olivia and Orsino like Viola because she is dressed as a man. Do they really like men? Or do they like women?

We see Olivia change her feelings quickly. She likes Cesario, then Sebastian. She sees Viola as a sister, not a lover. She says, "You are my sister."

German rule in Africa was cruel. This is true for the Ovaherero and Nama people. They were hurt in German South West Africa. But not all of German rule was bad. German rule was different in each place.  Education was also different. When Britain took over German East Africa, many Africans could read and write. People said German schools in Kamerun were good.  

South West Africa was different. The government did not help to teach Africans there. Instead, they asked churches to teach the Africans. The government did help to teach Europeans. They built schools for them. This made a big difference in South West Africa. Most people could not read or write. Many things caused this. This paper looks at why South West Africa was different. We look at what settlers and leaders thought about Africans.

There are many books about schools in German Africa. Most books are in German. They were written a long time ago. Some books compare schools in different places. 

One book talks about schools in South West Africa and East Africa.  This book says that South West Africa was different because it had many settlers.

South West Africa had good weather for settlers.  More settlers lived there than in other German places.

Popular music has many types. It is hard to list them all. Some types are rock, rap, country, jazz, and folk. Each type has many small types. Heavy metal is one type. It is loud and strong. It has many small types, too. 

Heavy metal music is old. It started many years ago.  People like it because it is strong and has many feelings. It can be sad or angry.

Heavy metal is like a movement. It is not just music. It is a way of life. 

Some people say heavy metal is dark. The music is loud and fast. It has many strong sounds. The words are often about sad things.

People who like heavy metal like the dark sound. They like the strong music. They like the sad words.

Long ago, a man named Henri Rousseau paint. He paint things that look like dreams. He paint a big picture called "The Dream". This picture show a woman in a dream. It also show Rousseau's own dreams. Rousseau want people to like his art. He want to be famous. 

Rousseau was not a rich man. He work for the government for many years. He did not go to art school. Rousseau be sad when his wife and children die. He start to paint to make him feel good. He paint pictures of people like him. 

Rousseau want to be a good painter. He want the art world to like him. But the art world is hard. Many good painters live at the same time. Rousseau paint in a way that is not like the other painters. He paint in a way that is simple. He want to be part of the art world.

Many smart people think that ethics and art are close. They think truth and beauty are close too. I think there is a good reason for this. John Keats said, "Beauty is truth, truth beauty- That is all / Ye know on earth, and all ye need to know." We learn many things in school and from life. But we seem to like ethics and art without learning them. 

Ethics and art try to say what is, not what should be. We study art and good acts to know why they are good. We do not study them to know how to make good art or good acts. We can talk about art and good acts. But we can not say all about why they are good. When you like a book or painting, you might say, "There is something about it."

Art and morals can not be fully described. Flannery O'Connor said, "A story is a way to say something that can not be said any other way." We can describe a book. But there is more to it. I think art and morals have something special.

Ethics and art are both felt deeply. We feel them, but we can not always explain them. Literature is special because it has morals. We need morals in life. We need them in books too.

Germany is a strong country now. It has one culture. This culture is in many places. It is in München near the mountains. It is in Kiel by the sea. It is in Köln by the Rhine River. It is in Dresden by the Elbe River. Germany has many parts. It has many groups of people.

The Germans live in a land called Germania. No one knows for sure where the name came from. A man named Tacitus said a group called the Tungrians were called Germans. They fought the Gauls. Julius Caesar used the word "Germanus". He used it to talk about groups that fought him. He got the word from the Gauls. Caesar said the Germans fought the Gauls often.

Some people say the word "German" comes from a spear. The spear was called a "ger". Some say it comes from a word that means "to shout".

Tacitus wrote about the Germans. He said they were different from other people. He said they did not mix with other people. He said no one would want to live in Germany.

The Romans fought the Germans. They took things from them. They also used German soldiers in their army. The Germans lived near the Romans. They traded with them.

I look down. I see the thing in front of me. My mind is empty. I look at it. I know what I see. But I do not think about it. My mind is fast. It sees. It goes.  I think, but I do not think much. I am like a machine.

Once, I read a book about how to draw. The book is called "The New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain." I want to draw. I was six years old when I first wanted to draw. The book teaches how to see. 

The book says to make a box around the thing you want to draw. This makes a big thing small. For example, a bowl of fruit on a table in a room. The box makes it just the bowl of fruit.

I look at the thing in front of me. I want to make a box. But I cannot. I am too amazed. I am like an artist. I see things in a new way.

I take a tool. My hand moves. I want to make art. The water is clear and green. It moves slowly. I want to be a good artist.

My hand hits the thing in the bowl. It does not move. I am angry.

I clean. I am sad. I am tired.

Teenagers die in car crashes. Many things cause this problem. The National Institutes of Health say teen brains are not ready to drive. Teenagers are also very new to driving. This leads to more crashes. Teens also crash more when friends are in the car.

Some states have rules for new teen drivers. These rules limit when teens can drive. They also say teens can not drive with other young people.

But these rules are not enough. Teens are not ready to drive. Doctor Marvin Zuckerman says 18 is too young to drive. He says teens want to take risks.

We need to wait longer to let teens drive. We need to keep teens safe. If we do not, more teens will die.

We need new laws. Schools can still teach teens about driving. But no one under 18 can drive.

Teens can still get a permit before they get a driver’s license. They still need to practice driving.  The number of practice hours should be the same as now.

I looked at old Edison films. There were fifteen trick films from 1895 to 1901. These films use good ideas to show tricks. I looked at how the films are made. I also looked at a few films that are different.

Most trick films are made in one place. The camera does not move. The films use long shots and medium shots. Each shot is one film. 

Many trick films use a stage. The camera looks at the stage from the front. The actors move side to side. They do not walk to or from the camera. For example, in the film *Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel* (1900), the actors walk back and forth.

The camera does not move. This means the shots are long. Close-up shots are not used. 

Most trick films are short. They are less than one minute long. They show quick tricks. They do not tell a long story.  

Sometimes a trick film has many shots. But the viewer sees them as one shot. For example, in *The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots* (1895), the camera shows many shots. But the viewer sees them as one shot.

John Taylor like the idea of the United States. He want the United States to be good. He think the United States can make good rules. John Taylor was a farmer. He work on a farm. He also work in government for a short time. He like the idea of people having freedom.

John Taylor think the best job is farming. He think farms are good for people. He want the government to help farmers. He want the government to be small. He think the government should not have too much power.

John Taylor think people are good and bad. He think the government should help people be good. He think the government should not stop people from doing good things.

John Taylor think the Constitution is important. He want the government to follow the rules in the Constitution. He think the government should not make new rules. He think the Declaration of Independence is also important.

Figure 17 show a big drop in log reports in the third month. This was sad. We do not know why this happened. In winter, few people go to school by bike or by foot. This may be part of the reason for the drop. December is the end of the fall school time. People are busy with school work. They may not think about the log reports. December is also a time for holidays. Students and teachers are off from school for a month.  They do not need to go to school. School starts again in late January.  This may be why there are few reports in January.  

We do not know why there are few reports in February. New things are exciting at first. This may be why reports were low. We made a special week for carpooling in March. We wanted to make the project fun again. This worked. More people sent in reports.

One problem is that people like to drive. This is part of our culture. We need to give people reasons to use other ways to get to school. We gave out prizes, like gift cards. We should give away bigger prizes, like bikes or cars. This may help more people join.

We gave the same prizes all the time. We should give bigger prizes later in the project. In December, we could say we will give away bikes. In January, we could say we will give away a car. This may help more people join.

An ETF is like a basket of stocks. You can buy and sell it on the stock market.  It is like a stock. It tracks things like the value of many stocks or the price of gold. ETFs are good for money. They cost less than some other ways to buy stocks. You can buy just one share of an ETF.

ETFs have good parts. They have many stocks. This helps to keep your money safe. But ETFs also have bad parts. You must pay a fee each time you buy or sell an ETF.

This paper looks at one ETF. It is called IHF. We look at the ten stocks that are in IHF. We want to know if IHF is as good as buying those ten stocks by themselves.

We look at how much money is in each stock in IHF. We want to know if the ten stocks are good to buy together. We look at how much money they make and how much risk they have.

We find that buying the ten stocks by themselves makes more money. They also have less risk. But we need to know if this is very different.

We look at how much the price of each stock changes. We want to know if the ten stocks are very different from IHF.

Poe like the poem "Dream-Land". He use the word "Thulé" in this poem.  This word came from a writer named Virgil. Virgil use it for an island. The Greeks thought it was far away. Poe also like a writer named Goethe. Some say Poe copy Goethe's work.

Goethe write a very famous play called "Faust". In "Faust", there is a short poem called "The King of Thulé". The king in this poem lose his wife. He drink too much and is sad. He give his things to his kids. He go to a cliff and die.

The king in "The King of Thulé" is like the king in Poe's poem. They are both sad and alone. Some think Poe is sad about losing someone. "Dream-Land" and "The King of Thulé" are like friend poems. They talk about the same things.

Poe knew about Goethe. He like a writer named Tennyson. Tennyson like Goethe too.  Many people made copies of Goethe's work. So Poe could see it.

A man fell in a food store. He fell on applesauce. The store manager knew about the applesauce. He did not clean it up. 

Can the man get extra money from the store? The extra money is called punitive damages.

A judge may not throw out the man's case. The man must show the manager was bad. The manager knew the applesauce was bad. He knew other people fell. He did not care.

The manager was on a break. But the man will say this is not a good reason. He had time to clean the applesauce.

Many people fell in the store before. The manager did not fix the problem. The man will say this is bad.

The man was hurt badly. 

The law says the man can get extra money if the store was bad. The store was bad because it did not care.

Four years ago, I took a class about Islam. We talked a lot about if Islam is a bad religion. This is a big question now. After nine eleven, the news showed Islam in a bad way. Now, the news shows Islam in a good way. 

I did not think we would have a president with the name Barack Obama. He has Muslim family.

I read the story of the Prophet Muhammad. I think it is strange. I thought Muhammad was strong. He took over tribes and made them be Muslim. But the story says he was kind. People came to him and liked his ideas.

The story of Muhammad is like the story of Jesus. Muhammad made food grow bigger. This makes me think the storytellers want people to like Muhammad. They want to show him as a good man. 

There are many stories about people who became Muslim. But some stories are not from the people who saw it happen. This makes the stories seem less true.

I think the story makes Muhammad look good. But history shows he was not a good man. I think Muslims should know the real story.

Jesus teach good things.  Many people believe his words.  But after Jesus, people change his teach.  Now, people are more new and want to change things. Some old people want to keep things the same.  But many people want to know Jesus' real teach.  They want to go back to Jesus' way.  It may take time but it will happen. 

The church will be strong.  But now many kinds of churches are different.  In the future, all churches will be more like each other.  

History shows us big changes.  

Christianity was bad in Roman times.  But then Rome became Christian.  

Our country changed. Now African-Americans are strong leaders.  

Christianity will change again.  People will go back to Jesus' teach.  They will read Jesus' words in new ways.  

Long ago, there was only Judaism.  This is where Christianity came from.  

Jews believe in one God. They read old books. 

Jews were not all the same. They had different groups.

The book "The Jungle" shows that people want good things for them. They want more money and a good life. They do not care about people who are poor.

The owners of the big factories are bad. They want big factories. They do not care about people or the earth. Upton Sinclair writes about how the factories make black smoke that goes far away. The owners do not care about the smoke. They do not care about the animals.

The factory owners also do not care about the workers. They want more money. They make the workers work long hours. They fire workers when they want. The workers have no help. There are no good laws to protect them.

The workers are like slaves. They have no good life. They cannot escape.

Many writers use ways to make the reader feel a way about things. Some ways work better than others. F. Scott Fitzgerald uses many ways in his book *The Great Gatsby*. He uses words in new ways. He also uses things to have a special meaning. He does this with colors like gold, green, white, and red. In *The Great Gatsby*, Fitzgerald gives colors special meanings. He uses these meanings to make the reader think about things in a special way.

Fitzgerald uses white and gray to mean the same thing: being alike. White is good and fancy. Gray is old and weak. Fitzgerald shows this at the start of the book. People wear white a lot. Daisy and Jordan are always in white. Nick wears white to Gatsby's party. Tom wears a white shirt. Catherine is white. The only time people do not wear white is when Nick sees Gatsby's party. There are many colors there. Fitzgerald also uses white and gray for simple things. Nick goes down "white roads" to work. People at Gatsby's party are just "gray names" on a list. Catherine's house is like a "white cake". Fitzgerald also calls plain people and places white or gray.

Fitzgerald uses white and gray to show that things are not important or are the same. He does this with Daisy. After not using white or gray for a long time, he describes Daisy in a "white car". Now, Daisy seems like just another thing. Gatsby wants her. Fitzgerald uses white and gray more with Daisy to show this. Daisy has a "gray fur collar". She wears white to meet Tom and Gatsby.

San Diego is good for farming. The weather is warm and sunny. People grow many things there. They grow tomatoes, oranges, lettuce, squash, broccoli, herbs, peaches, lemons, berries, honey, and peppers. Many people want to buy food from farms that do not use chemicals. These farms have long waiting lists. People like to buy organic eggs and milk. Many farms give tours. People can walk, look at birds, and do other things there.

This kind of farm can help the earth. It can also make money. Farms can help animals have a good home. They can teach people about farming.

Organic farms are good for animals and plants. They do not use chemicals. But they cost more to run. These farms need more work. They need people to take care of the plants and the bugs. 

This farm is near the town of Potrero. It is part of a plan to protect animals and plants. Many animals live there. Some are in danger of going away.

People lived on this land a long time ago. They raised cows and sold wood. Now, a farmer might want to grow food there. 

I looked on the computer to see what helps farmers. I found an organic farm near there.

Culture is big in talks. Culture is hard to show. It is not same for every person. Saying all Russians are like this or all Japanese are like that is not good. It is better to know how culture is good for talks. How does it help or hurt?

When you talk to people from a new place, you see it like your own place. You make comparisons. To learn about a new culture, you can study its past. You can learn its rules. You should not judge or change it. You must accept it. You must work with it, especially in talks. If you are not strong in talks, you must be extra good to the new culture.

Culture is not just for countries. Companies have their own cultures. Some work long hours. Some work less. You can see culture in how people dress. You can see it in how they talk. You can see it in who they hire.

Some companies like to help people. Other companies only help certain people. You can see this in America. Different companies are different. This shows you that there are many ways to be part of a culture.

Values are very important. They show why people do things. If people value saving face, they will not be rude. If people value hard work, they will not give up easily.

Before you talk to people, learn about them. Learn about their culture. Learn about their values. Then you can talk better.

The fool say, "There is no God." This is from the Bible. The Bible is a holy book. This saying start a talk by Saint Anselm. He talk about God. Saint Thomas Aquinas also talk about God. We want to know who has the good talk. 

Both men say God is real. We will say God is real for this talk. We need to talk about one kind of God. Our two men talk about this God.

Saint Anselm say we can know God in our head. God is in our mind. We can think about God. We can see God in our mind. This is like faith. Faith is when we know something is true even if we can not see it.

Saint Thomas say we can know God with our head and our eyes. We can see God in the world. We can see things and know God made them. This is like logic. Logic is when we use our head to know things.

Both men have good points. But neither man show us all the proof we need for God.

Long ago, a man named Buddha was born. He was a prince. Buddha grew up and left his life. He found a new way to live. He taught other people his way. This way is called Buddha’s teaching, or Buddhism. Buddhism is old. It is more than two thousand five hundred years old.

Buddhism is different now. It is not the same as when Buddha was alive. People still follow Buddha’s teaching. They do this in many ways.

In Sri Lanka, people have a special event. It is called the water-cutting ceremony. Monks and people who are not monks do this. They do it to show their belief in Buddha. Buddha did not say to do this.

Buddhism has changed over time. This is normal.

There are ways to talk about the changes in Buddhism. We can talk about things inside Buddhism and things outside Buddhism. We can talk about things that hurt Buddhism and things that do not hurt Buddhism.

Buddhism is about many things. 

Buddhists believe in three things. They are the Buddha, the teaching, and the group of people who follow the teaching. The teaching is in books. There are many books. They have rules for how people should live. They also talk about things that are important to understand. 

Buddhists want to end suffering. They want to end the cycle of life and death. They want to be free from bad things like wanting, anger, and being confused.

The United States and Mexico were once rivals.  This rivalry went on for fifty-seven years, from 1836 to 1893. The rivalry was very strong. The highest point was the Mexican-American War. This war was from 1846 to 1848. The United States won the war. The United States took Texas and the American Southwest. There were many fights between the two countries. The rivalry stopped before World War I.

The rivalry started because Americans and Mexicans had different ideas. They had different ideas about religion, culture, and way of life. They also had different wants. This is like many other countries that are near each other. Countries that are next to each other often have problems. 

David M. Pletcher said, “Only in Mexico and Cuba are there big problems for the United States.” This is true. Mexico and Cuba are close to the United States. They have been rivals to the United States. Other countries in Latin America have good relations with the United States.

Religion was a big problem between the United States and Mexico. Many countries have had problems with religion in the past. Sally Frahm said, “In the 1800's, Americans did not like Catholicism and monarchy.” This is like the Cold War. The United States and the Soviet Union had different ideas. They also wanted different things.  

The distrust between the United States and Mexico came from the past. The English and Spanish did not like each other. This made it hard for the United States and Mexico to be friends. 

Diehl and Goerts said there were seventeen problems between Mexico and the United States. Most of the problems were about land. There were fights on the border. Bandits from the United States went into Mexico.

Schmitt said the rivalry stopped when Mexico needed the United States. The rivalry ended when the United States wanted to help Mexico’s economy.

Fifteen years ago, I got sick. The sickness was new. I did not know I had it. I was a nurse. I chose this job for safe-ty. As a child, I did not have safety. People said, "You can always work. People get sick." So, I chose nursing. I liked to be a scientist or a writer. But I chose nursing.

Now, I am 46. I am alone. I have no money. I can not work. I am still sick. I get money from the government. I have nothing left. Every day is hard. My safety and my feeling of being good are gone.

I know I could not live without my family and friends. They help me. I know that when bad things happen, you need help.

Life has emergencies. Big ones and small ones.

We need to help each other. We need to trust each other. We need to ask for help.

Some people say America was built by strong people, alone. But strong people need help too. Our ancestors helped each other. They shared. They cared.

I am ready for bad times. I have food, water, and tools. But I also know my neighbors. We help each other.

Why do living things change? Are there limits to how they change?

A scientist named D’Arcy Thompson said long ago that we do not know how to describe even simple living things with math. This is still true today.

Math can help us understand how things change over time. We can use math to study how shells change. 

We looked at pictures of the shells of a type of seashell called Prunum. We used a computer program to make new shell shapes. These new shapes show us the limits of how shells can change.

A shell is like a tube that spins. It makes circles called whorls. The whorls are around a center line called the columella. The whorls can grow fast or slow. The line between the whorls is called a suture.

The biggest whorl is the last one. The tip of the shell is the apex. The opposite end is the base. The animal lives inside the shell through an opening called the aperture.

We can look at shells from different angles:

* Apical view: Top of the shell.
* Basal view: Bottom of the shell.
* Apertural view: Opening of the shell is facing us.
* Abapertural view: Opening of the shell is away from us.

To count the whorls, look at the top of the shell. Find the first suture line. Draw a line down the shell. Count the whorls on each side of the line.

A shell grows by adding new parts. We can use math to track how the shell grows.

Indonesia’s child and mother death rate stay the same for ten years. Indonesia will meet many goals. This is good. But, child and mother health is not good enough. Indonesia needs to help.  Indonesia has more births with a worker.  Seventy-two percent of births have a helper. This is good. But, many helpers are not doctors. They can not help if a birth is bad. This is why many mothers die. 

Indonesia has less sick children. This is good. But, many sick children do not see a doctor. 

Cesarean births are low. This is bad. More city births are cesarean. Rural births are less. This shows a problem. Cities have better help.

Poor people use less help. This is bad.  Poor people can not pay for help.

Indonesia needs to help more. Should Indonesia use many small plans? Or, should Indonesia make the whole health system better? Small plans are easy to do. But, they can make other parts of health worse. Small plans can make things more hard to do.

Victorian books are like this: they have lots of details. They talk about rich people. Two books are from this time, but they are not like other books. These books are *Oliver Twist* and *Wuthering Heights*. These books have mystery. They also have strange things. This makes the people in the books more real. We can see why they do things. 

This is from *Oliver Twist*:

"Many thoughts came to his mind. They were strange and hard to understand. He walked between two men, Sikes and Crackit. They were angry and talking. He heard their words. Then he saw himself talking to them. Suddenly, he heard a loud noise. Shots! People cried out. Lights were bright. He felt dizzy. Then he fell. All around him was noise. Someone took him away. He felt hurt. This pain did not go away. It stayed with him."

These books use mystery in dreams. Sometimes the dreams show us what is inside a person. In *Oliver Twist*, the dreams show us Oliver's pain. They show us what he knows.

In chapter 28, Oliver has a dream. He is shot. He remembers the shooting. He feels like he is dreaming. He wants help. This shows that Oliver has no power. He cannot control what happens to him. He is weak and sick. His pain is constant. He is afraid. He does not know who hurt him.

The shooting shows that Oliver has no control. He cannot even try to help himself. He is sad. Fagin, a bad man, makes him sad. Oliver gives up. If he was not sad, he would try to save himself.


*Wuthering Heights* is also a book with mystery.

"The day passed. It was gone quickly. Night came. Night was long and quiet. It was also short. It was night again."*

Two years ago, I worked in a school program. I helped young students with school work. I liked to help them with reading and writing. One boy, Adrian, needed help. He was in third or fourth grade. Adrian had hard time reading. He knew some words, but not others. It was strange. Adrian spoke good English. His mother came to the school one day. She did not speak English. I spoke very little Spanish. We talked a little. I knew then that Adrian could read, but he did not know the English letters well. I do not know if this helped him much.

I tell this story because language is a problem in schools. Many children speak Spanish. Reading can be hard for them. We must help these children. We can help them learn English. Tutoring can help. But we need more. We need many ways to help.

We can have schools with two languages. This helps all children. It helps them learn. Some people think this is a bad idea. They say it costs too much. This is not true. All children can learn from this. 

We do not need all teachers to speak two languages. But we can have helpers who speak two languages.

We learn about big things when we are small. Some go to school, some go to church. Some find the good things inside. Many people like the good things they see in their family. Some people say no to these good things. They say there is only what we see. We can like one thing, then like another. We all look for good things in life. We want to find light in the dark.

My father said a red bird was his favorite. We sat on our porch. It rained hard. The rain made a loud sound. He looked at the rain. He looked sad. He was thinner. His hair was less. He did not look at me. I felt sad. I wanted to talk, but I did not. It would be too hard. I hugged him and sat close. We looked at the rain.

My father died in December. He was sick for a long time. He did not get better. He was sad. I did not know why God made him suffer. I did not pray. I did not think God was listening.

I did not want to watch my father die. I did not want to see him go. I wanted to remember him when he was strong. I knew my father well. I knew he did not want me to watch him die. I stayed in bed for three days. No one called me.

The "Gothic Novel" is old and new. It is like two words that do not match.  Ian Watt said this in his book, *The Rise of the Gothic Novel*. Writers say bad things about the Gothic. They also say good things. Some say it is not deep. Others say it is very good. They say it shows something strong and scary. This is from Burke.

The first Gothic Novel was *The Castle of Otranto*.  Horace Walpole wrote it. It used old ways of telling stories and new ways. He wanted to make a new kind of story. Walpole used old ways from plays and new ways from stories. He called it "A Gothic Story."  

Gothic stories use old ideas from plays, buildings, and ways of life. 

Even when *The Castle of Otranto* was new, the word "Gothic" was old. People thought it was old-fashioned. They thought it was not good like new things.

Gothic stories are old and new at the same time.  They use old ideas and new ways of telling stories. 

One old idea in Gothic stories is chivalry. Chivalry is about being a knight.  Walpole liked chivalry. Knights were brave, good, and strong. He thought people were not like that anymore. 

Walpole wrote *The Castle of Otranto* when things were bad in England. He was worried about the future. He may have thought that people were not good anymore.

He wrote about a man named Frederic. Frederic was brave. He was a prince. He was sad. He was supposed to be dead.

He was like a knight. He was strong and good.

Supply chain help make good go from buyer to customer. It start with the buyer order, then get the things to make the good, make the good, and send the good to the buyer. A man named Keith Oliver said the word "supply chain" in 1982. He say it is how a company plans, does, and checks every step to make the buyer happy.  

There are six parts to a supply chain: make, get, store, place, move, and talk. Managers use these parts to help buyers.

Making is the first part. It is the start of the whole chain.  Managers need to know what buyers want. They look at the market to see what buyers need. Then they decide what to make and how much. 

Managers also decide where to make things. They think about the best place to make good things well and fast. They also think about how to help buyers. After they decide, they plan work and take care of machines. Making is very important. 

The next part is getting things. Managers decide how to get the things to make the good. They can use their own workers or ask other companies to help.

Ellen Page is on a street. She has a sign. The sign says, "Hitler is alive in Burma." Burma is a country in Asia. It is a place with a strong leader. This leader came to power a long time ago. People in Burma had protests in 2007. Monks led the protests. They wore yellow clothes. The protests were called the "Saffron Revolution."  The leader did not like the protests.  He sent soldiers. The soldiers hurt people. 

This is not new. Leaders sometimes hurt people. This has happened for a long time. 

In China, people protested in 1989. The leader sent soldiers. Many people died.  

In Rwanda, people were killed. This was a bad time.

Hitler was a leader who hurt many people.

Duke Ellington make good jazz music. He make music for long time. He good at make music for his band. He play piano good. But he best at make music for other people to play. He make music with many parts. Some parts for one player. Some parts for all players. Ellington make music sound good together.  He know how to make each player sound good. He make music sound new and special.

One song is called "Creole Love Call." It use voice like an instrument. Ellington use voice to make music sound good. He make music sound rich. He help his players sound good too.

"Creole Love Call" have six parts. Each part is different.  First part, voice and woodwinds talk back and forth. Voice start smooth, then get rough. Second part, trumpet play a slow solo. Third part, clarinet play fast. Fourth part, whole band play like first part. Fifth part, woodwinds play fast again. Brass and drums stop and start. Sixth part, voice and woodwinds talk back and forth again. Voice sound rough like growl. Then there is a short part at the end.

Ellington use voice to make music sound good in many songs. In "Hot and Bothered," trumpet and voice talk back and forth. This make music sound good. In "It Don't Mean a Thing," trombone play the first part.

She want some thing. She did not know what. This want start when she was fourteen. She was a young girl then. She is now seventeen. She want a person, not a thing. But she no like any boys. Some boys like her. They try to talk to her. But no one good for her. She think about this a lot. Why she no like boys? She think about this for years. But she no have good idea. She live her life. She think about want all the time.

Her home is peace. Her parents are good. They no fight. They no fight with her much. They only fight about her being free. She is the child of calm people. But she is fun and happy. People like her. 

Today is not peace. She walk in her home. She want to do some thing new. She hear a small cry. It is her mother. She run to the kitchen. "Mom! What wrong?" Her mother is on the ground. She say "Ow" in small breaths. Her daughter put her hand on her mother. "Ouch...sweet...need you to go to the hospital." Her mother say this fast. Her daughter know she hurt bad. "Okay Mom, where can I pick you up?" Her mother show her. Her daughter is strong. She take her mother to the car. She put her in the back. She drive.

The hospital smell bad. It smell like sick people. But she not think about this. She think about her mother. She run to the nurses. She say "Help!" Some doctors come. They put her mother on a bed. They take her away.

Her mother fall off a step stool. She try to get a vase.

This study look at how eating a "Mediterranean Diet" help women. The study used a score to see how much women eat like the Mediterranean Diet. A high score mean more like the diet. 

The Mediterranean Diet is high in plants. It has fruits, nuts, whole grains, and beans. It has good fat and fish. It is low in meat and bad fat. You can have some wine. 

Other studies show the diet is good for the heart. This study look at strokes and death from strokes. 

The study followed 74,886 women for 20 years. The women were healthy. They told the study team about what they ate. The team used this to make a diet score.  

The team looked at many things that could change the results. They looked at age, how much women smoke, weight, and if they took medicine.

The study found that women who ate like the Mediterranean Diet had less heart disease and strokes. They had a lower chance of dying from heart disease or stroke.

The USA had a big money problem in 2007.  Many people lost jobs. Houses cost less. Many big companies had no money. This problem is still here. We must ask: how did this happen? How can we stop it? 

The problem was bad choices by people in power. They told banks to give many small loans. These loans were bad. The banks gave out too many. The banks made things worse by selling these loans to others. When people could not pay back the loans, the banks had no money. The banks made other people lose money too.

This problem started long ago. In 1999, the president wanted to stay in office. He made it easy for banks to give out loans. This was a bad idea. A writer for the New York Times said this would be bad. He was right.

Many new things made the problem worse.  New kinds of loans were made. These loans were very hard to understand. People took out many loans. They bought many houses. This made the housing market very big. Then the housing market went down.  Many banks lost a lot of money. Some big banks had to close. The USA had to help the banks.

Exposition is hard. It can be boring for readers.  Exposition is when you tell the reader things.  "Show, don't tell" is good advice.

Dr. Merlin does not like too much exposition.  She likes stories with action.

Exposition is like when one person tells another person many facts.  It is not as good as showing the facts in the story.

For example, a story might say a woman met her husband. They got married. Then he died.  This is not very interesting.

It is better to show the woman and her husband. Show how they love each other. This makes the reader care about the husband. When he dies, the reader will be sad.

Writers need to show, not just tell.  They need to give the reader details.  The reader should feel like they know the characters.

I look at two news shows from Columbus, Ohio. The first show was NBC 4. It was live this morning (August 13, 2011). The main story was about a man in Ashley, Ohio. He hurt his wife. They did not say her name. His name was Shad Hostettler. They showed his picture. He looked mean. They talked about this story for two minutes. They said he hurt his wife many times. He is in jail. I think they talked about this story for the right amount of time.

The next story was about a man named Travis Buyers. He was 18 years old. He was hurt in Sharon Woods. He was very sick. No one knows who did this. The police are looking. This story was short. I think this is because he was a black man. I see this often. When a black person is hurt, the news does not talk about it much. If a white person is hurt, the news talks about it a lot.

The next story was about a hole in a helicopter. Someone shot at the helicopter. They said the bullet was small. Crime Stoppers is offering five thousand dollars for information.

The next story was about the rain. It will rain on Saturday. It will be hot this weekend. The news talked about this for a short time. They wanted people to watch more news.

The next story was about a robbery. A man robbed a store. He was black. He wore a sweatshirt. He was tall and skinny. The news talked a lot about his race.

The next story was about a man named Rene Rodriguez. He was in jail. He sold drugs. The news said he was in jail for 300 months. I do not know why they said that. They also said he was Hispanic. I do not think this was important to the story.

Brothers have a strong bond. This bond is strong and hard to break. There are many feelings in this bond: love, pride, jealousy, and meanness. Brothers know each other better than anyone else. They see themselves when they look at their brother. 

A brother's true feeling comes out in bad times. These feelings can have a big cost. To understand these feelings, you must deal with the results. When you look at your brother, you see your real self. You see yourself as you are, not how others see you. Your actions show your true character. 

The story "The Scarlet Ibis" shows these things. Two brothers go on a hard trip in a nice place. They have big feelings of sadness and pride. Only one brother lives. The story shows the brothers' feelings in many ways.  

The main brother feels a lot of pride. He wants a brother who can learn from him. He wants to teach him to run, jump, and climb. He wants a brother to play with. Doodle, his little brother, is sick. He cannot do these things. The main brother is sad. He is even angry. He thinks of hurting Doodle. But then Doodle smiles. The main brother feels better. He loves Doodle.

The mind is very hard to understand. We use words to talk about it. Old words are not good. We used to say the mind is like a tablet, then paper, then a book. Now we say it is like a computer. This is not good.

The mind takes in new things. The eyes see light. The ears hear sounds. The skin feels things. These things change to signals. The mind then works with these signals.

The mind looks at small parts of things. Then it looks at the whole thing. Look at a black box on white paper. The mind sees the color, shape, and edges. Then it knows it is a box. The mind also uses what it already knows.

The mind picks what is important. It pays more attention to some things. You see many things when you look at your shoes. But you do not see each blade of grass. You hear your name in a loud room. The mind picks it out.

The mind keeps things. There are different kinds of keeping. Some things are kept for a short time. Other things are kept for a long time. Words are kept in different ways. We keep how they look, how they sound, and what they mean.

There are many ways to talk about how the mind works. Some ways use computers. Other ways use how people remember things. One way is to say that the mind has ideas. These ideas are like points. They are joined if they are related.

Aldous Huxley writes about bad things. Technology and money are bad. He writes about this in his book Brave New World. People in the book like their group. They like to be happy. They learn to be happy all the time. 

The people in the book are like toys. They do not think for them selves. A man called the World Controller tells them what to do. If we look at the book in a special way, we see Huxley does not like how money works.

He uses big words like "homogeny" and "reification." These words mean things are the same. Huxley thinks this is bad.

Huxley shows how money can be bad. He uses a word called "false consciousness." People do not know the truth about money. They only care about getting more. This is how the World Controller keeps the people happy.

The World Controller is like a leader. He tells the people what to think and do. The people like him. They do not know he is controlling them. 

The people in the book do not have friends. They do not love each other. They do not feel strong emotions. They only care about things. Huxley shows this to us.

I go to school at University Park. I have been a student for two and a half years. Many students have a problem on campus. It is hard to get around. My first year, I lived in East Halls. It is far from the center of campus. I had to walk to class. It took a long time. I talked to a person who went to school here long ago. He said East Halls was far from the rest of the school. Now, there are new things there.  The school is growing. It is harder to get around. 

What is the best way to get around? A bike is good. But the school needs to be good for bikes.

I have a friend. He rides a bike now. He said he likes it. He said bikes are good. They are fast. You can ride a bike far.

I live far from school now. I bought a bike. It saves me time. I can go to class fast.

There is a road near my home. It is not good for bikes. I have to walk sometimes. I do not have time to walk a lot. My bike is good for me.
